# ─── Avietho Digital — environment variables ───
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill the values for local development.
# `.env` is in .gitignore and will never be committed.
#
# NOTE: Only variables prefixed with VITE_ are exposed to the browser.
# Anything else stays server-only (which we currently don't have).
# Do NOT put secret keys here if they need to stay private — those
# require a backend / proxy. The values below are safe-by-design to expose.

# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID.
# Safe to expose: designed for client-side use. Protect by restricting
# property access + referrers in the Google Analytics console.
VITE_GA_ID=G-Y7PB4CJ73D
